description	"Shadowtrooper

^2Weaponry:
- Lightsaber
-- Medium / Strong Styles
-- Saber / Gun Defense (2)
-- Saber Deflect (2)
-- Saber Throw   (1) ^3[CS1]

^6Inventory:
- Cloaking Device

^5Force Powers:
- Jump  (2)
- Push  (2)
- Sense (1)
- Lightning (1)
- Grip (1)

^8Attributes:
- Cortosis Armor (1)
- Force Block (2)
- Force Focus (1)
- Reinforcements (1)
- Assemble (1)

Shadowtroopers were stormtrooper-Dark Jedi hybrid soldiers created by the Dark Jedi Desann and Imperial Admiral Galak Fyyar. Similar to the Reborn soldiers, Desann used the Valley of the Jedi to imbue stormtroopers with Force powers. Shadow armor also had limited optical stealth capabilities via personal cloaking and was constructed out of cortosis, a rare mineral capable of resisting lightsabers. This made them tougher to defeat in lightsaber combat."